subtitleNullable: Pokemon matchups based on their basic stats
descriptionNullable:
### Context

This dataset was worked for the development of a prediction algorithm using Logistic Regression for the Concurrent Programming course.

### Content

The dataset contains the information of a 1 vs 1 of pokémon battles, including the versions of the new generations up to the Galar region (without considering the expansion passes). For the evaluation of the winner, only the basic stats and possible type advantages are considered, so for the moment we forget more complex concepts such as: natures, special stats, abilities and others.

### Inspiration

Pokemon always caught my attention and I found the idea of ​​working with the possibility of their existence and how their direct confrontations would unfold in an open environment.
